Pretty bad run, haven't played the game in a few months, but my internet went out so I decided I would finally actually record and submit a run, this was my second attempt, first one was 1:08 

I think that the first half wasn't so bad, especially mirror temple, that was pretty good all things considered, but towards the end, I think my fatigue started to kick in (that one room in resurrections where I spent like 2 minutes lmao). 

I think my best run was like a 0:53 or so but that was several months ago and it wasn't a valid run I believe. 

Anyways, yeah, Celeste is great, it'll be nice to finally have an *official* time on the leaderboards, even if it's not the greatest
